From Stephen Holland Subject Re Annual inguinal hernia repair In article Porter Clark wrote synopsis Young man with inguianl hernia on one side repaired now has new hernia on other What gives he asks and he Of course my wife thinks it's from sitting for long periods of time at the computer reading There is the possibility that there is some degree of constipation causing chronic straining which has caused the bowel The classic problems that are supposed to be looked for in someone with a hernia are constipation chronic cough colon cancer and you're not too young for that and sitting for long periods of time at the computer reading Good Luck with your surgery Steve Holland